  "title": "*Perm* Safety Officer, HSE (Oil & Gas)   - East ( up to $4000 inclusive of allowance) #NJE",
  "description": "<ul><li>Promotes Safety culture in the workplace.</li><li>Responsible for the preparation, compilation and maintenance of safety manuals to ensure compliance with safety regulatory standards that meets the Company’s HSE policy and objectives.</li><li>Responsible for ensuring the Safety Management System is maintained and properly followed to comply with internal, customer, and regulatory requirements, and that it meets the Company’s HSE policy objectives.</li><li>Continuous review of the HSE Manual and its’ implementation.</li><li>Promotes good HSE practices and ensures these practices are in place and safety regulations followed.</li><li>Conducts investigation of accidents and near miss incidents reported.</li><li>Organizes and conducts HSE training plans.</li><li>Intervenes in unsafe activities or operations.</li><li>Other adhoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p>Joy Yeow Zhi Qian<br />(CEI Registration No:R2096261)<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA Licence No: 99C4599)</p>",
